{"tid":1230272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"馬鐵上見到個黑衫揸白花嘅絲打","createTime":"2019-06-16T07:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T09:34:44.000Z","uid":259244,"like":5,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3990a1a9c2af4368627321bdb91152125fd995eb","tid":1230272,"uid":259244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uRHnUO3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuRHnUO3.png&h=4ea04aa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到呢位絲打真係眼都濕晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我買唔到花又唔識摺 唯有買包菊花茶請巴打飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打我地今日行埋你嗰份<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不撤不散維園見</span></span>"},{"pid":"4f4274f0b8f80be69bc7e513e33a38acdeee17a5","tid":1230272,"uid":229955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:01:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大會宣布 提前出發 @ 14:30 <br />\n<br />\n1) 由維園 去 金鐘添美道<br />\n2) 2 條 BANNER : 「痛心疾首」 「撤回惡法」 由宗教界 同 一班媽媽帶領<br />\n3) 「痛心疾首」 BANNER 會放喺適當地方 , 畀各市民獻花<br />\n4) 有宗教界負責安排 祈禱會<br />\n5) 有支援抗爭者基金籌款箱<br />\n<br />\n616 黑色大遊行 五大宗旨:<br />\n<br />\n1) 撒回惡法<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n2) 釋放被捕既抗爭者<br />\n3) 我們不是暴徒<br />\n4) 追究黑警開槍責任<br />\n5) 淋病下台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警冷血，林鄭殺港<br />\n無線新聞，出賣港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7e36de3c1310cb3b51a03c925849fb6f0c318b","tid":1230272,"uid":1374,"like":85,"dislike":1,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:01:37.000Z","msg":"死狗公 影你老